        dd (成) 事一作：是。招引麻煩或禍端。→製造糾紛。(<ruby>因<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄣ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>為<rt>&thinsp;ㄨ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>愛<rt>&thinsp;ㄞ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>插<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄚㆴ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>閑<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/閒)<ruby>事<rt>&thinsp;ㄙㄨ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>引<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄣˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>起<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄎ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>是<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>非<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>討<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄜˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>費<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨ丨˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>氣<rt>&thinsp;ㄎ丨˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>丌<rt>&thinsp;˙ㆤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>載<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄞ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>戴<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄞ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>事<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>事<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄞ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>情<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)。→<ruby>是<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>講<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㆲˋ→ㄍㆲ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>做<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄨㆤ˪/ㄗㄜ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>人<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄤˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>無<rt>&thinsp;ㆠㄜˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>安<rt>&thinsp;ㄢ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>分<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㄣ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>守<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄨˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>己<rt>&thinsp;ㄍ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。類語：惹：招，～惹。引，惹。逗，引～。挑，～逗。

